</span><span class="c29 c20">Summary</span><span class="c32">:<br></span><span class="c5 c1 c33">Software and/or UI Development and Design. 10+ years professional experience in both Design, Commerce,</span><span class="c1 c33">&nbsp;Financial</span><span class="c5 c1 c33">&nbsp;and Software related industries. JavaScript with </span><span class="c1 c33">associated frameworks </span><span class="c5 c1 c33">and other web technologies (listed) </span><span class="c1 c33">were essential in development for all of my work described below</span><span class="c5 c1 c33">.</span></p><p class="c6 c19 c30"><span class="c1"></span></p>
<p class="c6 c30"><span class="c29 c20">Skills &amp; Expertise<br></span><span class="c7">Expert</span><span class="c15 c42">&nbsp;</span><span class="c20 c29"><br></span><span class="c4">&raquo;</span><span class="c29 c20">&nbsp;</span><span class="c17">HTML + HTML5 and 4.1+</span></p><p class="c6 c30"><span class="c4">&raquo;</span><span class="c29 c20">&nbsp;</span><span class="c17">CSS 1 | CSS 2 | CSS 3</span></p><p class="c6 c30"><span class="c4">&raquo; </span><span class="c17">JavaScript 1.8.5 + JScript/EcmaScript versions 3,4, and 5</span></p><p class="c6 c30"><span class="c4">&raquo; </span><span class="c17">ActionScript 2.0/3.0</span></p><p class="c6 c30"><span class="c4">&raquo; </span><span class="c17">PHP &#8536; + mySQL and Microsoft SQL</span></p><p class="c6 c30"><span class="c4">&raquo; </span><span class="c17">HTML DOM/XML DOM Core fundamentals</span></p><p class="c6 c30"><span class="c4">&raquo; </span><span class="c17">XML + XSLT for Data and Dynamic Content</span></p><p class="c6 c30"><span class="c4">&raquo; </span><span class="c17">Android SDK Using JAVA for APK Development</span></p><p class="c6"><span class="c1"><br></span><span class="c7">Advanced</span><span class="c15 c42">&nbsp;</span><span class="c29 c20"><br></span><span class="c4">&raquo; </span><span class="c17">C++/C#<br></span><span class="c4">&raquo; </span><span class="c17">ASP, .ASPX, .NET Framework<br></span><span class="c4">&raquo; </span><span class="c17">Java SDK<br></span><span class="c4">&raquo; </span><span class="c17">Python, Perl + SSH<br></span><span class="c4">&raquo; </span><span class="c17">Haskell, LISP, D, Haxe, and other non-common Software API&rsquo;s</span></p><p class="c6 c19 c30"><span class="c1"></span></p><p class="c6 c30"><span class="c29 c20">JS Frameworks<br></span><span class="c17">Highly adept with previous usage</span></p><a href="#" name="58d61ceab429b0735f25151fff83cde9985d5b6b"></a><a href="#" name="0"></a><table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" cla